snippet: The shootings took place on Tuesday, after Tibetans had gathered to protest the detention the previous day of a respected village leader.
abstract: Chinese police officers open fire on Tibetan protesters, wounding at least 10 people.
lead_paragraph: The shootings took place on Tuesday, after Tibetans had gathered to protest the detention the previous day of a respected village leader.

headline.main: At Least 10 Injured After Police Fire on Tibetan Protesters
